sources.description:
After a mental breakdown from her toxic city job, a young female game developer finds solace as a rural cryptominer in California. While coding, she stumbles upon a mysterious message from an unknown origin. In her investigation, she faces cyberattacks and ominous encounters which turn into a fight for her life, forcing her to her secret bunker where she takes drastic action.
2024.  Stars: Mikayla Iverson, William Benedict, Charla Bocchicchio
